rows.label: tev072501_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Nan'celeg about life on the Ma-non ship.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Nan'celeg if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Nan'celeg about the Ganglion attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Nan'celeg about the Ganglion attack.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0001
rows.name:
There was something quite similar to those capsule
pods where we were being held by the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0002
rows.name:
But the Ma-non are far beyond the Ganglion when it
comes to designing for comfort.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0003
rows.name:
Not only do the pods here scan for any sign of ill
health in their occupants, but they always maintain
a perfectly comfortable temperature.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0004
rows.name:
And you can access a wide variety of information
from the terminals within.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0005
rows.name:
If only there was a way to grow the plants we eat
inside of them, they would be absolutely perfect.
But perhaps that would be asking for too much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0008
rows.name:
May I ask you a question? When you're in this city,
do you feel a clear connection with your internal Ovah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0009
rows.name:
Lately, I've felt that my own Ovah is beginning to dull.
It can sometimes be hard to tell what it wants of me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0010
rows.name:
...What? You humans don't have any sort of Ovah
within you at all?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0011
rows.name:
Th-that's...incredible. We Orphe could suffer almost any
torment, but losing our Ovah is something we could
never endure![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0012
rows.name:
I must say I admire how you're able to act with such
confidence when you're completely bereft of an Ovah's
warmth and guidance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0030
rows.name:
When I'm within this city, the war with the Ganglion
feels like something happening on a distant world.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0031
rows.name:
So when I heard you had suffered a Ganglion attack
recently—and was shown footage of their onslaught,
no less—I was terrified.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0032
rows.name:
At times like these, my Ovah should be urging me to
replicate myself out of sheer survival instinct.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0033
rows.name: But my Ovah is silent. I don't understand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0038
rows.name:
My Ovah retains memories of being held by the
Ganglion...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0039
rows.name:
And when I experienced actual fighting and faced the
prospect of my own death, I was terrified.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0040
rows.name:
At times like these, my Ovah should be urging me to
replicate myself out of sheer survival instinct.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0041
rows.name: But my Ovah is silent. I don't understand.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Nan'celeg about the new Orphe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Nan'celeg about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0024
rows.name:
We're seeing a gradual increase in individuals like
Nen'celeg.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0025
rows.name:
For example, Non'barac from the industrial district is
working with Orphean Technologies so that humans
can fight more effectively.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0026
rows.name:
Though they are both the new type of Orphe, we can
see the difference between them in the way Nen'celeg
prioritizes her own intellectual curiosity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0027
rows.name:
I wish Nen'celeg understood that there are more
productive things she could research than her division
parent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0019
rows.name:
Excuse me, but when you look at Nen'celeg,
do you experience a cloudy feeling in your chest?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0020
rows.name:
...No? Then this must be some peculiar characteristic
of my own.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0021
rows.name:
Nen'celeg believes this could be an experience called
"love," but I am unsure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0022
rows.name:
All I know is that this unsettling feeling is getting
steadily worse.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev072501_MSG0023
rows.name:
Dear me. I wonder if we Orphe will truly be okay if we
continue producing new offspring like this.[ST:wait ]
